&lt;p&gt;Located in the heart of Madrid between the  famous Gran Va and Puerta  del Sol. With FREE WiFi, free bike rent, safe, plasma TV with DTT, daily press...!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Perfect location to visit all the main cultural and architectural attractions of the city, including the Puerta del Sol, Palacio Real, Plaza Mayor, Madrid de los Austrias and the museums El Prado, Reina Sofia and Thyssen.
Found at just 2 minutes walking distance from the recently inaugurated train station in the Puerta del Sol, from where you can reach the Barajas Airport (for just 2) and the Atocha train station (for just 1).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enjoy whit the best shows just a few meters from all the main theatres like as  Principe Gran-Va Theatre, flamenco shows and the best shops in the city such as the El Corte Ingls, H &amp; M, Mango, Zara, etc ... as well as the most famous restaurants and tapas bars. In font of Telephonic build, Fnac and Prisa.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The metro station Gran Via is found a few 50 meters from the hotel takes you directly to the AVE train station (Atocha Renfe) and Barajas airport, as well as many city bus lines and tours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By staying in our hotel during this year will enjoy a free glass of Spanish wine and an exquisite tapa in the department stores El Corte Ingles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And if you travel with your pet, we will provide bedding and feeding bowls free of charge!!!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All double and single rooms include free WIFI connection,  26 flat screen televisions with international channels, hydro massage showers and free safety boxes. Double or twin beds available with exterior or interior views (on request).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All family rooms (with capacity up to 4 persons) ideal for families or groups of friends, include free WIFI connection, 26 flat screen televisions with international channels, hydro-massage showers and free safety boxes.Double or twin beds available(on request). 
All superior rooms, are whit king bed and include free WIFI connection, personal computer whit internet connection, 26 flat screen televisions with international channels, hydro-massage showers and free safety boxes.
The hotel also has rooms available for persons with reduced mobility, contact whit a fornt desck.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do not hesitate to contact us for any special preferences you may have.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The hotel offers the following FREE services:
 Personal computer on request
WIFI connection in all rooms and communal zones
Daily Press
Safety boxes (with capacity for a laptop)
Hydro massage showers in all rooms.
Information on local excursions, city maps, reservations for shows and restaurants.
Two internet points for public use.
Free bike rent.
Luggage room.
Cots and buggies for kids on request.
Complementary bedding and food bowls for your pet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Special discounts for our clients:
20% discount in the public parking in the Plaza del Carmen, (minimum 24 hours) please ask at the reception for more details.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Body Factory gym offers an special discount for our guests.
Take advantage of our two free internet points, found in the reception area, and our free bike rent to get to know the city in a unique and original way!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ask our friendly staff for advice on the best shopping and dining areas, and for reservations for local excursions and shows. Dont hesitate to contact us if you are travelling with your pet or have any other special requests  we will do our best to assure that your stay is a pleasant and comfortable as possible!&lt;/p&gt;

